{"pk": 41, "path": "00010001000600010001", "depth": 5, "numchild": 0, "title": "On Puzzles", "draft_title": "On Puzzles", "slug": "puzzles", "content_type": 23, "live": true, "has_unpublished_changes": false, "url_path": "/welcome/magazine/puzzles/puzzles/", "owner": 1, "seo_title": "", "show_in_menus": false, "search_description": "", "go_live_at": null, "expire_at": null, "expired": false, "locked": false, "first_published_at": null, "last_published_at": null, "latest_revision_created_at": null, "live_revision": null, "body": "

Organelles, cells, organs, organisms, families, cultures, planets \u2013 these bodies nest within each other in irregular concentricity, one within the next, each encased by its own semi-permeable boundary. In the jigsaw puzzle of incarnation, all the pieces slip and slide, expand and contract, ignite and extinguish, push, pull, infiltrate, and emerge. There, but for the grace of God, go I. Wondrous beings abound all around, in places where I am not.

fields.body: Organelles, cells, organs, organisms, families, cultures, planets – these bodies nest within each other in irregular concentricity, one within the next, each encased by its own semi-permeable boundary. In the jigsaw puzzle of incarnation, all the pieces slip and slide, expand and contract, ignite and extinguish, push, pull, infiltrate, and emerge. There, but for the grace of God, go I. Wondrous beings abound all around, in places where I am not.

fields.description:
With Shelley Tanenbaum and Sara Wolcott: Summoning gardeners and prison justice reformers, mystics and peace advocates for a time of deep listening stemming from our interconnections. Through history, story-telling, and worship-sharing, we seek an ecology of hope, ways of integration and action.

Location: Ben Lomond Quaker Center, Ben Lomond, CA

For more information, see: www.quakercenter.org/programs
Intermountain Yearly Meeting consists of Arizona Half Yearly Meeting, Colorado Regional Meeting, and New Mexico Regional Meeting.
North Pacific Yearly Meeting consists of Montana Gathering of Friends, Pacific Northwest Quarterly Meeting, and Willamette Quarterly Meeting.
Pacific Yearly Meeting consists of College Park Quarterly Meeting and Southern California Quarterly Meeting, as well as monthly meetings in Hawaii and Mexico.
